                     <interp inst="t18790915-851-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="animalTheft"></interp>, Stealing a mare, the property of <persName id="t18790915-name-552" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18790915-name-552" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
